               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Taʾammǝra Māryām “Miracles of Mary” (fols. 3ra-76ra, 78rb-82rb)
                     I-1) Maṣḥafa śǝrʿāt, Introductory rite of al-Muʿallaqah (fols. 3ra-6va)
                     I-2) Taʾammǝra Māryām: 76 miracles (fols. 6va-8va, 11va-76ra, 78rb-82rb)
                     I-3) ʾƎsaggǝd laki wa-ʾǝweddǝsaki … “I worship Thee…” (fols. 8va-9rb l.5)
                     I-4) Introductory exhortation and hymns (fols. 9rb l.6-11rb)
 I-5) ʾAkkonu
                     bǝʾsi… “Does not the man…” (distributed among the miracles of Mary, fols.
                     12va-48ra)
 II) Taʾammǝra Mikāʾel “Miracles of Michael”: 4 miracles (fols.
                     76ra-78rb)
 
 Additio 1.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">

                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>Some miracles in Text I-2 are followed by an ʾarke-hymn:</note>
                     <note>- ለዘዘነብር፡ መነኮስ፡ በደሴተ፡ ጤግሮስ፡ ፈለግ። … (<locus target="#48vb">48vb</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- ለፊላታዎስ፡ ኤጲስ፡ ቆጶስ፡ ሰሚረኪ፡ ጽድቆ። … (<locus target="#51rb">51rb-</locus>va)</note>
                     <note>- ከመ፡ ጸሐፈ፡ ደቅስዮስ፡ ተአምረኪ፡ እሉደ። … (<locus target="#52ra">52ra</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- ብእሲ፡ አረማዊ፡ ኀበ፡ ሥዕልኪ፡ ተሪቦ። … (<locus target="#53rb">53rb-</locus>va)</note>
                     <note>- መበለት፡ ሠናይት፡ ጊዜ፡ ትጸሊ፡ ጸሎተ። … (<locus from="54vb" to="55ra">54vb-55ra</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- ግርማ፡ ተአምሪኪ፡ እግዝእትየ፡ ጥቀ፡ ይበድር፡ ፍጥና። … (<locus target="#56rb">56rb</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- ሰሚዖ፡ ሕፃን፡ ለእሙ፡ ገዓራ። … (<locus target="#59ra">59ra-</locus>b)</note>
                     <note>- ብእሲ፡ አረማዊ፡ መዝገበ፡ ዓመፃ፡ ወእከይ። … (<locus target="#66vb">66vb</locus>)</note>
                     <note>- እምድኅረ፡ ሞተት፡ ወለት፡ ዘትሰመይ፡ ዲና። … (<locus target="#70vb">70vb</locus>)</note>
                     <note>Text I-4 includes the hymns:</note>
                     <note>- ʾO-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl ba-kǝlʾe Māryām walādita ʾamlāk ʾǝmmu
                        la-ʾǝgziʾǝnä ʾIyasus Krǝstos kahāli … “O my Lady, Holy Two-fold Virgin Mary,
                        Godbearing, Mother of our Lord Jesus Christ the Almighty …” (<locus target="#10vb">10vb</locus>, l. 4-19)</note>
                     <note>- salām laki ʾo-ʾǝgzǝʾtǝyä qǝddǝst dǝngǝl ba-kǝlʾe Māryām walādita ʾamlāk
                        ʾǝmma bǝrhān ʾǝmma qʷǝrbān … “Salutation to you, o my Lady, Holy Two-fold
                        Virgin Mary, Goldbearing, Mother of the Light, Mother of the Eucharist…”
                           (<locus target="#10vb">10vb</locus>, <locus from="19" to="11ra">19-11ra</locus>)</note>
                     <note>Text I-5 comprises 32 strophes, which are strophes 1-31, 33 according to
                        GrohHymn pp. 336-51.</note>
                  </msItem>
